    "And what resources does it need (Sect. 6)?",
    "We break each of these questions down into more specific sub-questions, list options, and discuss how they could affect the board's ability to reduce risks from AI.",
    "The paper concludes with a summary of the most important design considerations and suggestions for further research (Sect. 7).",
    "ResponsibilitiesThe first and most important design choice is what responsibilities the board should have.",
    "We use the term \"responsibility\" to refer to the board's purpose (what it aims to achieve), its rights (what it can do), and duties (what it must do)."
